5:
I've been waiting for you, Shuilong!
Today's the day I finally BEAT YOU!
17:
I! LOST! AGAIN! AAAAAGH! After all
that training I did in other worlds, 
I still lost!
21: I hate to admit it, but... she's tough.
25:
But I lasted longer than before! Next
time, I'll be quicker on my feet!
Maybe then I'll actually get a hit in!
35:
I-I'm not having fun! This is serious
business, okay?! I'm here to get
revenge!
42:
...I just need to gain more
experience... Yeah, that's it!
45:
Hey, Alk. Do you know any good
places to train? Like... like a really
intense dojo, or something!
52:
How about we go for a change of
pace, instead?
64:
*sigh*... Do I really have time for this?
I know it's important to rest once in a
while, but...
67:
I get why you'd want to keep
training. But Shuilong isn't the type
of opponent you can defeat by just
charging full speed ahead and
hoping for the best.
75:
...I get it, okay? I know I shouldn't be
rushing things.
78:
The thing is, I really, really like
competing. Like, I LOVE strategizing,
entering tournaments, and getting
the upper hand. It's so much fun!
81:
...But right now, I need to focus on
my mission.
83:
The problem is, I'm getting nowhere
even though I'm taking this seriously.
86:
Sorry. You must be tired of my
complaints! It's my mission, and it's
my responsibility.
90:
No need to be sorry. I'm half doing
this for myself, actually. Someone's
gotta knock Shuilong down a peg or
two.
94:
You got that right! And... thanks. For
bringing me out here.
97:
Dang it! I could've sworn that was
the Big One!
99:
Man, that kid never quits. Just keeps
on tryin' to catch the Big One.
105:
Just a big ol' fish that lives 'round
these waters... At least, that's the
rumor.
107:
It ain't no rumor! And I'm gonna
catch the Big One, just you see!
109:
You've been sayin' that for damn
near three years, boy. Champ's a
stubborn one, for sure.
124: Hey, uh... I think you've got a bite.
130:
What the heck?! Why... is this thing
so strong?!
134:
All right everyone, on the count of
three! One... two... THREE!
159:
Sorry about that, miss. You must be
soaked...
162:
It's nothing! I've been meaning to
get a little exercise in, anyway!
164:
But look at you! You finally caught
the Big One!
167: Huh? That ain't the Big One, miss.
171:
Seriously?! THAT big thing isn't the
Big One?
174:
Huh. I never would've guessed. 
All that effort for nothing...
177:
What are you talkin' about? It was
lotsa fun!
179:
Thanks for fishin' with me today.
That kick sure was something else!
182:
Heh-heh. I got plenty more where
that came from.
185:
I'm gonna have lots of fun fighting,
too!
190:
Whew, look at the time! I haven't
had a day off like that in ages!
Thanks again, Alk.
194:
Don't mention it. Glad to see you're
feeling better.
198:
Of course! That was the most fun
I've had in a long time.
201:
Do you think, maybe I should... have
fun... when I'm fighting her?
204:
That's something for you to decide,
Fuulan.
207:
...But I think doing it that way suits
you more.
214:
Alrighty! Starting tomorrow, I'm back
at the grind!
217:
You better watch your back,
Shuilong!
